Look, I'm asking nicely.

2011
01:46:13,635 --> 01:46:14,760
Let me have your blood.

2012
01:46:15,969 --> 01:46:16,844
Oh, you want my blood?

2013
01:46:17,969 --> 01:46:18,677
[Chuckling]

2014
01:46:26,677 --> 01:46:27,427
Then come here...

2015
01:46:28,344 --> 01:46:29,219
and take it yourself.

2016
01:46:34,677 --> 01:46:35,552
Tommy...

2017
01:46:37,260 --> 01:46:38,302
Come on.

2018
01:46:55,135 --> 01:46:58,760
[Breathing Heavily]

2019
01:47:00,802 --> 01:47:03,760
[wolf howling]

2020
01:47:09,510 --> 01:47:11,635
[Grunts]

2021
01:47:51,260 --> 01:47:53,427
[wolf howling]

2022
01:47:53,677 --> 01:47:56,635
I am... I am Bhediya!

2023
01:47:56,719 --> 01:48:00,135
I am... I am Bhediya!

2024
01:48:00,219 --> 01:48:02,969
I am... I am Bhediya!

2025
01:48:10,802 --> 01:48:12,760
[Grunts]

2026
01:48:14,010 --> 01:48:17,219
